The paper deals with large scale learning problems and proposes a new algorithm that is parallel in both the selection of blocks and the selection of elements of the training set. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) category. Additionally, the paper involves stochastic optimization and numerical evaluation, which are relevant to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Numerical Analysis (cs.NA), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories.
